{"word":"G928 - βασανίζω - basanízō - bas-an-id'-zo - Pain","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βασανίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>basanízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>bas-an-id'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Pain"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேதனைப்படு, அலைவுபடு, வருத்தப்படு, வாதிக்கப்படு, வேதனையடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to test (metals) by the touchstone"},{"paragraph":"2. to question by applying torture"},{"paragraph":"3. to torture"},{"paragraph":"4. to vex with grievous pains (of body or mind) to torment"},{"paragraph":"5. to be harassed, distressed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G931 - βάσανος - básanos - bas'-an-os/931\">G931</a>; to <i>torture:</i> - pain, toil, torment, toss, vex."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G928 - βασανίζω - basanízō - bas-an-id'-zo/928\">G928</a>, <a href=\"#/G929 - βασανισμός - basanismós - bas-an-is-mos'/929\">G929</a>, <a href=\"#/G930 - βασανιστής - basanistḗs - bas-an-is-tace'/930\">G930</a>, <a href=\"#/G931 - βάσανος - básanos - bas'-an-os/931\">G931</a>"}]}